        And over the years, I kept learning (even diving into low-level
        programming, <ExternalLink
          name="6502 - Wikipedia"
          url="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MOS_Technology_6502"
        />) until I stumbled on Web Development, from which I discovered my love
        for building things!
      </span>
      <span
        >Outside of coding, I play chess and table tennis (ping-pong). <em
          ><ExternalLink
            name="Backspin serve!"
            url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8pqkVXsk6Pw"
          />
        </em>
